Argentina seemed completely unfazed by the prospect of facing Bosnia, Iran and Nigeria in their World Cup group as they laughed and joked around in training on Friday.

Lionel Messi and his teammates were in very high spirits as they were put through their paces by coach Alejandro Sabella at their camp near Belo Horizonte.

The Barcelona superstar looked relaxed despite the huge weight of expectation on his shoulders out in Brazil, showing off his ball juggling skills and laughing heartily as Javier Mascherano fell flat on his back during a passing drill.

