Sabella is likely to play either Lavezzi or Higuain in a three-man attack with Messi and Aguero when they take on Bosnia in the Maracana on Sunday night.

Meanwhile, Colombia coach Jose Pekerman has tipped Messi to make a return visit to the Maracana on July 13 and lift the World Cup trophy.

